Stacking the data to create a Time Series Object

serie <- gather(serie, Month, value,- Year)

Creating the date column:

serie$Date <- as.Date(paste(serie$Year, serie$Month, "01", sep = "-"),
                         format = ("%Y-%b-%d"))
#serie
serie <- serie[order(serie$Date), ]
